text: The 2024–25 FC Liefering season is the the 13th season of FC Liefering in the Second league. Daniel Beichler, who was caretaker at the end of last season, is the new headcoach for this season. ==Squad == 2024/25 * Goalkeepers: 31 Valentin Oelz, 30 Salko Hamzic, 32 Sebastian Künstner, 41 Christian Zawieschitzky * Defenders: 2 Matteo Schablas, 4 Jannik Schuster, 5 John Mellberg, 19 Marcel Moswitzer, 38 Leandro Morgalla, 39 Rocco Zikovic, 14 Valentin Zabransky, 40 Jakob Brandtner, 44 Kristjan Bendra, 47 Julian Hussauf * Midfielders: 7 Soumaila Diabate, 11 Tolgahan Sahin, 10 Zeteny Jano, 8 Tim Paumgartner, 37 Tim Trummer, 21 Oliver Lukic, 6 Elione Fernandes-Neto, 17 Quirin Rackl, 27 Rüstü Erdogan, 29 Valentin Sulzbacher, 36 Marc Striednig, 45 Alessandro Ciardi * Forwards: 16 Luka Reischl, 15 Alexander Murillo, 22 Marco Brandt, 9 Phillip Verhounig , 28 Nicolo Turco, 20 Gaoussou Diakité, 43 Enrique Aguilar, 38 Oghenetejiri Adejenughure * Coaching staff: Daniel Beichler (Head coach), Yuki Miyazawa, Stefan Schoberer (Assistance coaches) Heinz Arzberger (Goalkeeper coach) ===Matches=== ==Friendly matches == ==References== Category:2024–25 in European football Category:FC Liefering
